The evidence with the title 'Air pollution scourge underestimated, green energy can help: U.N. ... ' says Apr 9, 2013  ... Air pollution is an underestimated scourge that kills far more people than AIDS and malaria and a shift to cleaner energy could  ... “ air pollution is causing more deaths than HIV or malaria combined , ” ... 3.5 million people die early annually from indoor air pollution and 3.3 million from outdoor air pollution . 
